  "title": "Property Executive",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Manage and maintain residential/commercial property sites as assigned</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular checks and inspection on grounds to ensure property is well maintained</li>\n  <li>Ensure building statutory requirements are complied</li>\n  <li>Review and recommend replacement/improvement plans for managed sites</li>\n  <li>Provide essential customer service support to the residents and owners</li>\n  <li>Identifies relevant tender notices and liaise with internal divisions, oversee the entire tender process (e.g. attending site briefing, costing provisions, quality proposal, tender submission / interview)</li>\n  <li>Approve and adhere to budgets and expenditures.</li>\n  <li>Maintain good relations with client, staff, contractors and visitors to the site</li>\n</ul>",
