    "uen": "200808602G",
    "description": "<p>Abacus Property is an ISO 9001: 2015 accredited industry leader with portfolio value of more than S$10 billion, 5000 units of mix developments, industrial, commercial properties and 10,000,000 sf of real estate under our management. We are in the process for an Initial Public Offering with market interest in Ghana, Nigeria, Vietnam, Indonesia and China.</p>    <p>We are ahead of the curve with over a decade of proven track record. We offer integrated solutions across the Real Estate value chain.  We are known by peers and clients as a technology driven company.</p>    <p>We pay attention in shortlisting the most meticulous and those with the right profile fit to achieve the best results. </p>    <p>The industries we are in offer great opportunities for clients to increase their growth - as well as for our staff to be the Apex Leaders of tomorrow. <br />  <br />  At Abacus Property, we nurture your career development. If you wish to be part of our growing and talented team, we want to hear from you. </p>  ",
